## üìç Pin Assignments

| GPIO Pin | Function | Connection | Notes |
|----------|----------|------------|-------|
| **GP0** | I2C SDA | BME280 SDA | Data line |
| **GP1** | I2C SCL | BME280 SCL | Clock line |
| **GP27** (ADC1) | Battery Monitor | Voltage Divider | Optional |
| **GP28** | Status LED | LED + Resistor | Optional |
| **3.3V** (Pin 36) | Power Out | BME280 VCC | Sensor power |
| **GND** (Pin 38) | Ground | Common Ground | All GNDs connect |
| **VSYS** (Pin 39) | Power In | 5V Regulator | Main power input |

