### 2B: Component Specifications

| Component | Specification | Example Part | Notes |
|-----------|---------------|--------------|-------|
| Solar Panel | 5-10W, 6V | Generic 6V 10W panel | Higher wattage for winter/cloudy |
| Battery | 3.7V Li-ion, 3000-5000mAh | 18650 cell (3000mAh) | Protected cell recommended |
| Charge Controller | TP4056 with protection | TP4056 + DW01A module | Must have load sharing |
| Voltage Regulator | 3-5V in, 5V out, 500mA+ | Pololu U3V12F5 | Buck-boost for stable output |

### 2C: Battery Voltage Monitoring

```
    Battery +                           Pico W
       ‚îÇ                          ‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê
       ‚îÇ                          ‚îÇ                 ‚îÇ
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ R1 (10kŒ©) ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îº‚îÄ‚îÄ‚óè GP27 (ADC1) ‚îÇ
       ‚îÇ                      ‚îÇ   ‚îÇ     Pin 32     ‚îÇ
       ‚îÇ                      ‚îÇ   ‚îÇ                 ‚îÇ
    Battery -              R2 (10kŒ©) ‚îÇ                 ‚îÇ
       ‚îÇ                      ‚îÇ   ‚îÇ                 ‚îÇ
       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¥‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îº‚îÄ‚îÄ‚óè GND         ‚îÇ
                                  ‚îÇ     Pin 33     ‚îÇ
                                  ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò

Voltage Divider Formula:
    V_adc = V_battery √ó (R2 / (R1 + R2))
    V_adc = V_battery √ó (10k / 20k)
    V_adc = V_battery / 2
    
    Therefore:
    V_battery = V_adc √ó 2
```

**Component Details:**
- **R1 & R2:** 10kŒ©, 1% tolerance (brown-black-orange-brown-brown)
- **Purpose:** Divides battery voltage (4.2V max) to safe ADC range (0-3.3V)
- **Power consumption:** ~0.2mA (negligible)

**Reading Battery Voltage in Code:**
```python
from machine import ADC, Pin

adc = ADC(Pin(27))
raw_value = adc.read_u16()  # 0-65535
voltage = (raw_value / 65535) * 3.3 * 2  # √ó 2 for voltage divider
print(f"Battery: {voltage:.2f}V")
```

### 2D: Power System Wiring Steps

1. **Solar Panel ‚Üí Charge Controller**
   ```
   Solar (+) ‚Üí TP4056 IN+
   Solar (-) ‚Üí TP4056 IN-
   ```

2. **Battery ‚Üí Charge Controller**
   ```
   Battery (+) ‚Üí TP4056 B+
   Battery (-) ‚Üí TP4056 B-
   ```

3. **Charge Controller ‚Üí Voltage Regulator**
   ```
   TP4056 OUT+ ‚Üí Regulator VIN
   TP4056 OUT- ‚Üí Regulator GND
   ```

4. **Voltage Regulator ‚Üí Pico**
   ```
   Regulator VOUT (5V) ‚Üí Pico VSYS (Pin 39)
   Regulator GND       ‚Üí Pico GND (Pin 38)
   ```

5. **Battery Monitor ‚Üí Pico**
   ```
   Battery (+) ‚Üí 10kŒ© ‚Üí GP27 (Pin 32) ‚Üí 10kŒ© ‚Üí GND
   ```

